                <note rend="inline" type="source">511.4R1/55: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Siam</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kaufman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-10-17T12:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 17, 1931—noon</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>27. Please inform Foreign Office that Colonel Lucien R. Sweet of the Philippine
                    Constabulary is being sent to Bangkok to assist Caldwell at Conference on Opium
                    Smoking.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
